THE REAL ISSUE: Groth16 Verifier in Solidity
======================================================================

Paper CLAIMED: ~40,000 constraints for recursive verification
REALITY:
  - Groth16 verifier needs ~20 MILLION constraints
  - Reason: Elliptic curve pairings must be computed in Solidity
  - Non-native field arithmetic: ~400 constraints per multiplication
  - 2 pairings × ~10M constraints each = ~20M total

Estimated Prover time for 20M constraints:
  - Single machine: 33.33m
  - 200-node parallel: 10.00s

Estimated Verify time (O(1)):
  - ~1.0 seconds per verification

